body_html:
Thank you for your feedback but tensorflow currently doesn't support raspberry pi.
This question is better asked on StackOverflow. There is also a larger community that reads questions there.

Or you might visit
https://petewarden.com/2017/08/20/cross-compiling-tensorflow-for-the-raspberry-pi/.
for more information.
Thanks!

body:
Thank you for your feedback but tensorflow currently doesn't support raspberry pi. 
This question is better asked on  [StackOverflow](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/tensorflow). There is also a larger community that reads questions there. 

Or you might visit 
https://petewarden.com/2017/08/20/cross-compiling-tensorflow-for-the-raspberry-pi/.
for more information.
Thanks!
